thread.title: Roxanne DeGrammont
thread.title_full: Craft Cuts reviewed by Roxanne DeGrammont

author: Roxanne DeGrammont
title: Roxanne DeGrammont
text:
I searched EVERYWHERE to find a wooden apostrophe to put at the end of my last name that we had put up in our home to no avail.
I came across Craft Cuts doing an internet search. They were extremely kind, prompt and professional. They made me the perfect wooden apostrophe for my wall and were extremely well priced. Thank you Craft Cuts!
